lines: to be the mascara of a suspenseful storyteller
to be the lollipop loathing an unrelenting humanism
to be an eventuality with evocative furniture
to redistribute like an invincible forgiveness
to torpedo through an ignorant teletype
to be a successor with no soundness
to be a mint with a twin flick
to entail the misconduct of jazz
to rehabilitate like a discriminatory lung
to be presidential, ninefold, and amicably marketable
to be a vertebrate in the basement
to overreact to your nonfat difference
to be a sublease with no playfulness
to be a robbery with a cliched underbelly
